findings.symptom: High host input time relative to step time
findings.likely_root_cause: Input pipeline bottleneck (host-bound preprocessing or IO)
findings.remediation: Increase input pipeline parallelism, enable dataset caching, and prefetch. Check CPU utilization and data source throughput.

findings.symptom: Batch size appears small for TPU throughput
findings.likely_root_cause: Conservative batch sizing or memory constraints
findings.remediation: Gradually increase batch size while monitoring HBM usage and step time. Use gradient accumulation for training if needed.
